item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Hollywood Undead - Comin' In Hot (Alternative Version) (FLAC)
item.description:
This is more of a shot in the dark but if there's any Hollywood Undead fans on here, you probably know that there's alternative versions of several songs floating around out there. Locating an MP3 version isn't super tough but I was wondering if anybody HAPPENS to have a FLAC version or if it even exists. I used to think it was just on a certain edition of American Tragedy but that's not the case.

If you're curious, there's also alternative versions of:

Undead, obviously
We Are
We Own The Night (music video version)
Hear Me Now (also music video version)

Again, not purchasable anywhere, just a shot in the dark here. Thanks anyways
